fulltitle: Jazz Guitar with Martin Taylor: 2-5-1 Progression
description:
Click here for more free sample lessons: http://bit.ly/2GAQTQK

In this sample lesson. Martin introduces you to the 2-5-1 progression, which is very important for jazz guitarists.
